    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API on autopilot for Follow-ups\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API on autopilot for Follow-ups. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual follow-ups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Normalize Contact Payload → Remove Duplicate Contacts → Enrich — Primary Provider → Primary Hit? → Merge Enrichment Paths → Score Enriched Records → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating follow-ups in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "2424467c-c234-a6a8-2848-97c28d9996a5",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
